Template: mythtv-controller/username
Type: string
Default: [root]
Description: mysql/mariadb user name:
 The user name used to connect to mysql/mariadb db
 in mythtv-controller.

Template: mythtv-controller/password
Type: password
Default: [password]
Description: mysql/mariadb user password:
 The user password used to connect to mysql/mariadb db
 in mythtv-controller.

Template: mythtv-controller/mariadb
Type: boolean
Description: Install mariadb:
 Install mariadb backend for mythtv-controller.
 If you do not now what to answer say yes.

